Bitcoin</head>
<body>
One of the most popular cryptocurrency created in 2009 by mysterious Satoshi Nakamoto.Transactions with Bitcoin provide full decentralization and have no central control. 
The value of this currency has increased significantly since 2011 and now its exchange rate is more than 2000 USD.
Everyone can use Bitcoin wallet to make everyday payments, to buy or sell currency. 

